{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"303a68e102","title":"邓小平九、十两月给中央的综合报告（节录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"00f1b42958","index":0,"year":1951,"month":11,"day":30,"articleId":"303a68e102"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f0e44655bb","name":"邓小平"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"93c39d5670","type":"title","text":"邓小平九、十两月给中央的综合报告（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"303a68e102"},{"id":"2f358cdf23","type":"authors","text":"邓小平","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"303a68e102"},{"id":"fa0a6289bf","type":"paragraph","text":"关于经济工作，均可照中央有关部门的计划执行，明年完成4万亿工商税收，估计也有可能，比较突出的是粮食问题，粮食不足的现象颇为严重。明年供应市场的粮食尚缺约7亿斤，加上准备外调1亿，共缺8亿斤，我们已决定用动员方式说服农民卖8亿斤给国家，能否办到，要看工作情形而定。……","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"303a68e102"},{"id":"6352d8480b","type":"paragraph","text":"土改及镇压反革命……在周兴同志报告中附带口述了杀（15万），关及劳改(20余万)， 管（10万）的数字。……","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"303a68e102"}],"page":{"id":"799b58285e","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"303a68e102","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}